title: Dan Soder & Shane Gillis: The Please Save Thibault Show
description:
Subscribe, rate, share, and leave a review! Subscribe to watch on youtube: barstool.link/KFCRadio In possibly one of the funniest and darkest episodes we've had to date, Dan Soder and Shane Gillis stop by. We talk about cat murder, fake legs, which animal you could take in a fight, and so much more. Let us know what you think on twitter: @KFCRadio @KFCBarstool @Feitsbarstool @DanSoder @ShaneMGillis


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kfcr
